def get_soup_from_url(url):
    res = requests.get(url)
    soup = BeautifulSoup(res.content, 'html.parser')
    return soup

URL_PAGE1 = "https://www.vendeeglobe.org/fr/classement"
def get_pages(url):
    soup = get_soup_from_url(url)
    urls = [url+"/"+i.attrs['value'] for i in soup.find_all('option')][1:]
    return urls
def get_files(url):
    for page in get_pages(url):
        try:
            soup = get_soup_from_url(page)
            URL = soup.find_all(class_="rankings__download")[0].attrs['href']
            r = requests.get('https://www.vendeeglobe.org'+URL, allow_redirects=True)
            open('data/'+URL.split("/")[2], 'wb').write(r.content)
        except : 
            continue
    return

def df_classement():
    dfs = []
    for filename in os.listdir("data/"):
        if filename == 'vendeeglobe_20210127_170000.xlsx' or filename == 'vendeeglobe_20210127_210000.xlsx' or filename.split("_")[1] > '20210127':
            continue
        data = pd.read_excel(f"data/{filename}",header=4,skipfooter=4,
                  names=['Unnamed: 0', 'Rang', 'Numro de voile', 'Skipper/Bateau','Heure FR', 'Latitude', 'Longitude',
                         'Cap', 'Vitesse', 'VMG', 'Distance','Cap1', 'Vitesse1', 'VMG1','Distance1', 'Cap2', 
                         'Vitesse2','VMG2', 'Distance2', 'DTF', 'DTL'])
        data.insert(5, 'date', filename.split("_")[1]+filename.split("_")[2].split('.')[0])
        data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], format='%Y%m%d%H%M%S')
        dfs.append(data)
    df = pd.concat(dfs, ignore_index=True)
    df.insert(3, 'Nom du skipper', df['Skipper/Bateau'].str.split('\n').str[0])
    df.insert(4, 'Nom du bateau', df['Skipper/Bateau'].str.split('\n').str[1])
    df = df.drop(['Unnamed: 0','Skipper/Bateau'],axis=1)
    df['Numro de voile'] = df['Numro de voile'].str.split('\n').str[1]
    df = df.replace('\n','',regex=True)
    df = df.sort_values(by=['date'])
    df = df.reset_index(drop=True)
    return df

def df_classement_final():
    data = pd.read_excel("data/vendeeglobe_20210305_080000.xlsx",header=4,skipfooter=4,
                  names=['Unnamed: 0', 'Rang final', 'Numro de voile', 'Skipper/Bateau',
                         'Unnamed: 4','Unnamed: 5','Unnamed: 6',"Date d'arriv", 'Temps de course','Unnamed: 9',
                          'Unnamed: 10','Unnamed: 11','Unnamed: 12','Ecart au premier','Unnamed: 13',
                         'Ecart au prcdent', "Vitesse sur l'ortho","Distance sur l'ortho",'pourcentage',
                         'Vitesse sur le fond','Distance sur le fond'])
    data = data.drop(['Unnamed: 0','Unnamed: 4','Unnamed: 5','Unnamed: 6','Unnamed: 9','Unnamed: 10',
                      'Unnamed: 11','Unnamed: 12','Unnamed: 13'],axis=1)
    data.insert(2, 'Nom du skipper', data['Skipper/Bateau'].str.split('\n').str[0])
    data.insert(3, 'Nom du bateau', data['Skipper/Bateau'].str.split('\n').str[1])
    data = data.drop(['Skipper/Bateau'],axis=1)
    data['Numro de voile'] = data['Numro de voile'].str.split('\n').str[1]
    data['Rang final'] = data['Rang final'].str.split('\n').str[0]
    data = data.replace('\n',' :',regex=True)
    return data

URL_PAGE2 = " https://www.vendeeglobe.org/fr/glossaire"
def df_voiliers(url):
    soup = get_soup_from_url(url)
    fiche = {}
    for i in range(33):
        key = ['Nom du bateau','Nom du skipper']
        value = [soup.find_all('h3', class_="boats-list__boat-name")[i].text,soup.find_all('span', class_="boats-list__skipper-name")[i].text]
        liste = soup.find_all(class_="boats-list__popup-specs-list")[i]
        for j in range(len(liste.find_all("li"))) :
            key.append(liste.find_all("li")[j].text.split(":")[0])
            value.append(liste.find_all("li")[j].text.split(":")[1])
        fiche[i] = dict(zip(key,value))
    return pd.DataFrame.from_dict(fiche, orient='index')

#rgression linaire entre VMG1 et le Rang 
X = df_jointure[['VMG1']].values
y = df_jointure['Rang'].values
X_train, X_test, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(X,y,test_size=0.25)
lr = LinearRegression()
lr.fit(X_train, y_train)
y_pred = lr.predict(X_test)
# Les coefficients
print("Coefficients: \n", lr.coef_)
# Mean squared error
print("Mean squared error: %.2f" % mean_squared_error(y_test, y_pred))
# Le coefficient de determination: (1 is perfect prediction)
print("Coefficient de determination: %.2f" % r2_score(y_test, y_pred))
# Plot outputs
fig = plt.figure(figsize=(15,6))
plt.scatter(x= X_test ,y= y_test,color='c')
plt.plot(X_test,y_pred, color ='b' )
plt.show()

Probabilit qu'un voilier arrive parmis les 10 premiers

In [78]:
#Monte Carlo Simulation
temp = df.groupby(['Nom du skipper']).agg({'Rang': ['mean', 'std']})
temp = temp.xs('Rang', axis=1, drop_level=True)
temp = temp.reset_index('Nom du skipper')
# number of simulations
sims = 1000
temp['monte_carlo'] = temp.apply(lambda x:np.random.normal(x['mean'], x['std'], sims), axis=1)
top_x = 10 
tmp_probs = pd.DataFrame((pd.DataFrame(list(temp['monte_carlo']),index=temp['Nom du skipper']).rank()<=top_x).sum(axis=1)/sims)
tmp_probs.reset_index(inplace=True)
tmp_probs.columns=['Nom du skipper', 'Probabilit']

y_pred = lr.predict(X_test)

# Mean squared error

print("Coefficient de determination: %.2f" % r2_score(y_test, y_pred))
